listing_company_name: Triple S Property Pty Ltd - WENTWORTH POINT
description:
Welcome home to this two-bedroom refinery nested above the sought-after Uno & Jade complex only 5 minutes walk away from Greensquare station and the chic inner-city dining district.

Soaking in double rays of sunbeam, this urban luxury highlights minimalism design sophistication with premium finishes, shaping an effortless flow of engagement around the open-plan layout interiors. Multiple home decor ideas are encouraged on the timber tile floors across every corner on top of the golden-sunlight adorned stylish inclusions. You will also enjoy overlooking the restful tree-lined neighbourhood views as you take a break from a day of busy schedule, as well as rewarding yourself with a gourmet meal made from the chef's kitchen equipped with intelligent stainless steel appliances.

Ideally located 5 minutes stroll away from Greensquare station, Woolworths, trendy local eateries, and Gunyama Park Aquatic and Recreation Centre. You will be indulged in an ultra-convenient urban lifestyle living in Zetland with close proximity to Sydney CBD.

About the property:
- Desirable Uno & Jade complex
- Dual aspects from North & West
- Open-plan layout, superbly finished interiors with timber tile pavement
- Sheltered entertainment balcony with tree-lined district views
- Chef's gas kitchen with a suite of European stainless steel appliances
- Generous bedrooms with mirrored BIW and timber tile floors
- Modern bathroom with sleek and shiny fixtures; One with a bathtub
- Concealed laundry & plentiful internal storage
- Air-conditioning; Security video intercom system; NBN internet
- One allocated underground carspace & storage cage
- Onsite building management at your service

Within 5 minute walking distance:
- Greensquare train station/ public library
- Woolworths Metro/ BWS liquor store
- McDonalds/ KFC/ trendy local eateries
- Gunyama Park Aquatic and Recreation Centre
- Bus stop to UNSW, Taylors College, USYD, inner-city and eastern suburbs

Outgoings (approx.)
Strata: $900/ quarterly
Council: $285.95/ quarterly
Water: $150/ quarterly

If you are interested in this property, please do not hesitate to contact us for more information and inspection arrangement.
